msg: [ABDERA-148] Support Java 6 compilation. Added "java6" Maven profile which can be invoke with mvn -Pjava6 installl or in settings.xml. Note: I also had to set  MAVEN_OPTS="-XX:MaxPermSize=128m" to avoid an out of memory exception when compiling with Java 6.
